reviewText: I love these Discovery channel collections.  I am sure that you will too.

The 5 dvds in the set: American Chopper : Jet Bike (Pilot) & Biketoper (2nd Pilot) - 92 mins. / Living With Tigers - 98 mins. / Dinosaur Planet - 98 mins. / Nefertiti Resurrected - 98 mins. / Jaws of The Pacific - 50 mins.

All 5 come in their own case, and they are all housed together in a cardboard slip box.

Audience Rating: NR (Not Rated)
